<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../styling/dynamicHomePage.css">
</head>

<style>
    * {
        font-family: sans-serif;
        margin: 0px;
        transition: all .5s;
    }
    h1{
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
    a{
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #3D3A68;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    a:active{
        background-color: rgb(34, 48, 175);
    }
    a:visited{
        color: #3D3A68;
    }
    a:hover{
        color: #d48234;  
    }


    nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        height: 10vh;
    }

    .logo {
        /* background-color: rgb(57, 133, 61); */
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color:#3D3A68;
        margin-left: 30px;
    }

    .nav-links {
        /* background-color: rgb(23, 206, 33); */
        width: 30%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-right: 70px;
    }

    .main {
        /* background-color: aquamarine; */
        display: flex;
        height: 90vh;

    }

    .main-col1 {
        width: 40%;
        /* background-color: beige; */
        display: flex;
        padding-left: 80px;
        padding-right: 40px;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .main-col1-content {
        /* background-color: rebeccapurple; */
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-left: 100px;
        margin-top: -100px;
    }
    .main-col1-content>h1 {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #3D3A68;
    }
    .main-col1-content>p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #3D3A68;
        font-size: 1.1rem;

    }
    button{
        background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #3D3A68 , #7772c0);
        color: white;
        width: 120px;
        height: 40px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 20px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    button:hover{
        box-shadow: 1px 1px 15px 1px #3D3A68;
    }


    .main-col2 {
        width: 60%;
        /* background-color: rgb(182, 182, 31); */
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .main-col2>img{
        opacity: 0.5;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width:600px) {
        
    }
</style>

<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">
            Haatey Kolomey
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a class="" href="/">Home</a>
            <a class="active" href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="">Contact</a>
            <a href="/login">Log in </a>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <section class="main">
        <div class="main-col1">
            <div class="main-col1-content">
                <h1>About this project</h1>
                <p>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Delectus dolore eaque nulla consequuntur rem, corporis commodi illum voluptate aliquam quam nostrum, tempore nobis cum blanditiis. Inventore velit qui nesciunt distinctio!
                    
                </p>
                <a href="/register"> <button>Sign Up</button> </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="main-col2">
            <img src="./cat01.png" alt="">
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>